title: CV App
subtitle: Front of a search engine on the content of previously downloaded CVs.
description:
Cv app is a cv search engine platform, helping HR to find quickly the perfect candidate by searching with simple or multiple keywords.
CVs can be uploaded with different formats such as PDF or DOCX. When uploaded, they are parsed and indexed in Elastic search DB.
